# Module: tf.raw_ops


<table class="tfo-notebook-buttons tfo-api" align="left">

Public API for tf.raw_ops namespace.

<!-- Placeholder for "Used in" -->


Note: <a href="../tf/raw_ops"><code>tf.raw_ops</code></a> provides direct/low level access to all TensorFlow ops. See   [the RFC](https://github.com/tensorflow/community/blob/master/rfcs/20181225-tf-raw-ops.md)
for details. Unless you are library writer, you likely do not need to use these
ops directly.
